Description: A R wrapper package for Weatherbit API. WeatherBitRWrapper can help you easily
    fetch weather data from Weatherbit API, including current weather, weather alert and 
    upto 16 days forecast weahter. You can fetch weather data based on city ID, city name,
    and postal code. It also support different languages and units. Enjoy our WeatherBitRWrapper!
